  "keyFeatures": [
    "High-throughput stream processing with Spark and Kafka",
    "Fault-tolerant ingestion with Dead Letter Queue (DLQ)",
    "Medallion architecture (Bronze/Silver/Gold) with Delta Lake",
    "Real-time analytics with ClickHouse OLAP",
    "Knowledge graph with Neo4j for relationship exploration",
    "Semantic search and RAG support with Pinecone vector database",
    "Change-driven sync logic for efficient downstream updates",
    "Production-ready deployment with Docker Compose and Kubernetes"
